{"tid":1648830,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼政府唔做嘢！香港人聲援爆眼記者","createTime":"2019-10-12T11:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T18:29:04.000Z","uid":139474,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e10ebb6f5aaca60bffd3ed7adeebdf18a02f4c78","tid":1648830,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"[再post過喺活動台]<br />\n印尼記者喺香港採訪被警方射中致盲，印尼政府唔理，香港人一定要理，一齊推返單嘢上國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n長話短說，下星期六搞返次遊行聲援好冇！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《追究警暴 守護記者》<br />\n日子：10月19日（星期六）<br />\n時間：1PM<br />\n地點：灣仔修頓-&gt;銅鑼灣印尼領事館</span></span><br />\n<br />\n琴日有印尼工人喺印尼領事館抗議，但得好少人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WjN8h5w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjN8h5w.png&h=15b1f6c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">印度政府無行動</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「主辦者之一的Sringatin表示，Veby遭到射擊後，印尼政府未有任何實際行動保護自己的國民，令印尼移工感到憂心。她表示，印尼政府和港府和中國政府都有經濟往來，因而選擇忽略他們的遭遇，她表示憤怒。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">假消息抹黑印尼姐姐收錢遊行</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「自10月初網上開始流傳「印尼姐姐每日收3000元參與示威後被捕」的假消息，其後更有印尼領事館官員轉發，警告在港印尼女工「你們什麼也不知道，別做多餘的事情。」Sringatin希望印尼政府可以澄清消息，並找出假消息來源，讓傳播假消息的人負上責任。」<br />\n<br />\n人哋嚟香港打工，報道畀印尼嘅人知香港發生咩事，都畀班狗搞到眼到盲埋，印尼唔理我哋香港人理！！一齊聲援印尼記者，遊行再諗方法眾籌，畀記者知道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">佢哋唔係Condom!!!!!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*遊行地點可以再傾，揀灣仔係因為印尼記者中槍地點喺灣仔，去印尼領事館係要畀壓力印尼理呢單嘢順勢推上國際"},{"pid":"7422e976d518de61418037ff1e1ae40eac9a2d2b","tid":1648830,"uid":159762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:30:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Hong Kong Police brutality database</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=b1401e83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nAvailable in Chinese and Japanese as well, please help spread the word!</span><br />\n<br />\n認真求推,搞左呢份野等三萬黑警都要接受國際審判<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1617815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1617815</a>"},{"pid":"94fb1b3b5aebb1bff70f4087fa98dc69db7f512e","tid":1648830,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:30:24.000Z","msg":"再post過"},{"pid":"0871b2682c3939aa2a41b20f9ec4a5d2621c1f6a","tid":1648830,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:30:45.000Z","msg":"plan定下星期行動"},{"pid":"1e214873fe69da7552cb6f7fd088a50854358548","tid":1648830,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:31:13.000Z","msg":"做好宣傳"},{"pid":"e5f1c184435f3992b5265c2b94bee244ce1387b1","tid":1648830,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:31:14.000Z","msg":"一句野解釋晒點解場運動會輸<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648803</a>"},{"pid":"2dc073432b98d3c322432ea563ce4e9efbf5b321","tid":1648830,"uid":64841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:31:25.000Z","msg":"點解唔星期日等多d姐姐可以join"},{"pid":"90eefddd55c73f80d1977ebeda3d0a9655606eaf","tid":1648830,"uid":271807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e10ebb6f5aaca60bffd3ed7adeebdf18a02f4c78","tid":1648830,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"[再post過喺活動台]<br />\n印尼記者喺香港採訪被警方射中致盲，印尼政府唔理，香港人一定要理，一齊推返單嘢上國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n長話短